{"tid":230464,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發現好多人睇完標題就唔係好睇內文","createTime":"2017-05-05T11:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T04:34:19.000Z","uid":55511,"like":15,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6fee3e8783e1e84963d1c4dbdf4aca467bd2e74","tid":230464,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"琴晚唔小心同fd做左 大家覺得點算<br />\n琴晚有個幾fd既男仔fd失戀 佢幾令仔 跟住叫我上佢屋企飲酒傾計 我地vodka,rum,啤酒,茅台 二鍋頭 清熱酷  jully sandy 春藥 咩都溝下來飲  結果唔使一個鐘兩個已經醉醉地同好high <br />\n<br />\n突然間佢係背後一野攬住我話 其實我鍾意你好耐  我果時唔識比反應佢 然後佢問我可唔可以錫佢一淡  <br />\n我竟然諗都無諗就錫左落去  結果我地越咀越激  互相纏住大家條頸  舌頭交纏住咁行左入佢房  一攤上床  <br />\n我地互相摷左陣大家就埋牙  詳細就唔多講  只可以講係幾開心  大家都射左兩次先攬住訓  我而家覺得好對唔住女朋友  同埋覺得同佢既友誼變左質  大家覺得應該點算?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 支持唔捐血<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:支持阿仙奴"},{"pid":"86fdba75b4992a4fdf6430de54c56a60a8a1fc38","tid":230464,"uid":68202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74374827a15143f7f5b3b8305cc90f4a37dac4d5","tid":230464,"uid":41811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07aaa0f9460ae0f8866b69b8c307e32003ed9d7","tid":230464,"uid":2660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:35:16.000Z","msg":"今日電話夠唔夠電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5392dc3f89a2039d101f45a76fda4e7e2e3335","tid":230464,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家連登仔或者香港人對睇post有幾厭惡,唔好話追post,連個post頭都好似懶撚睇到咁<br />\n係咪想連仔出voice mail功能呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.